http://www.openfl.org/documentation/getting-started/your-first-project/

$ haxelib install openfl
$ haxelib run openfl setup
$ openfl
$ openfl create project OpenFlHelloWorld
$ curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/openfl/openfl-samples/master/DisplayingABitmap/Assets/openfl.png > Assets/openfl.png
$ vim Source/Main.hx
# ...
$ openfl test neko
$ openfl test html5
$ openfl test flash
